title: Merkel India Visit to Focus on Berlin-New Delhi Economic Cooperation
text: The Make in India initiative and a free trade agreement will be key points in talks between Indian leadership and German Chancellor Angela Merkel during her upcoming visit to New Delhi, sources in the Indian Ministry of External Affairs told Sputnik on Friday. ...
